MaterialArticle.Title: 11 oz. Black Mug:Black / One Size
MaterialArticle.Description:
It means so much more with your own pet! Due to popular demand, we can now design YOUR cat, dog or any other pet for special use on our mugs. You'll love sipping your morning brew from this incredible mug featuring your very own fur baby. Or what an amazing gift to give to a loved one! How Does It Work?
Upload a high quality photo of your pet. Remember, we recommend a close and clear photo. Add to Cart and check out. Our expert designers will create a special design using the photo, just like the real life examples here. We'll create and ship your order to you.
Features:
Upload your own pet photo and our amazing designers will turn it in to the extra special breakout design - EXCLUSIVE TO US! The design appears on two sides of the mug Designed, printed and shipped from here in the USA!
This is an AMAZING DEAL and it’s so easy to add your own pet or whatever you like - cats, dogs, horses, birds... even people! HOW DOES IT WORK?Step 1Simply upload a HIGH QUALITY image of your pet. Make sure it's a clear image and it's been taken on the highest quality setting of your camera. Your pets face MUST be clearly visible and it helps to have its legs or paws out. It's also helpful if they're looking at the camera. We are unable to accept poor quality images as we won't be able to print and give you an excellent end result.You can also leave any instructions for our designer, such as "only use the dog on the right" or "keep paws out". This is optional and we will do our best - however the way these are designed doesn't always allow us to accommodate all requests. Click "Add To Cart" and complete the purchase process. Step 2Our expert designer will work to get your pet inside our special designs. Our designer does each design individually to get you the best results! Step 3Your design goes to our special printing process. Step 4We package and deliver to you as quickly as possible. We're confident you'll LOVE This Mug!!! CAN I ORDER MORE THAN 1 AT A TIME?Yes, it's very easy. Once you've added your first design to the Shopping Cart, simply click back to the product page and repeat the process. CAN I HAVE MORE THAN ONE PET IN THE SAME DESIGN?Yes, we can do our best but remember the size of each pet will not be the same as if you had just one in the design. We still recommend 1 pet per design. High quality ceramic mug Dishwasher safe Microwave safe Black gloss 11 oz. Decorated with full wrap dye sublimation

MaterialArticle.Title: Adorable 3D Cat Stickers:Black & White Tuxedo
MaterialArticle.Description:
This 2 pack of large cat wall stickers is purrrrfect for almost any surface. Put them on the fridge, the toilet seat, car, wall or anywhere else and you'll get a laugh every time you see it. Great for kids and adults alike. Exclusive to us (you won't find this anywhere else). The pack contains:
1 x life-sized semi-transparent vinyl water resistant indoor/outdoor sticker 1 x life-sized vinyl indoor sticker Packed in a retail pack Life sized at 9" x 11.5" (23cm x 30cm)
Suitable for any surface, these realistic stickers will put a smile on your face. Highly recommended for the fridge, walls, the bathroom, the garage, doors or even the car. Don't be fooled by imitations. Between the two decals in this pack, this cute fur baby will show on any surface - and it's only available here. Here at Winston & Bear, we manufacture these high quality sticker decals to the highest standard for customer satisfaction. Packed in a retail pack with full instructions, these are the perfect gift for the dog lover or just for decoration around the home or office. See Our Amazing Dog Stickers Here

This 2 pack of large dog wall stickers is perfect for almost any surface. Put them on the fridge, the toilet seat, car, wall or anywhere else and you'll get a laugh every time you see it. Great for kids and adults alike. Exclusive to us (you won't find this anywhere else). The pack contains:
1 x life-sized semi-transparent vinyl water resistant indoor/outdoor sticker 1 x life-sized vinyl indoor sticker Packed in a retail pack Life sized at 9" x 11.5" (23cm x 30cm)
Suitable for any surface, these realistic stickers will put a smile on your face. Highly recommended for the fridge, walls, the bathroom, the garage, doors or even the car. Don't be fooled by imitations. Between the two decals in this pack, this cute dog will show on any surface - and it's only available here. Here at Winston & Bear, we manufacture these high quality sticker decals to the highest standard for customer satisfaction. Packed in a retail pack with full instructions, these are the perfect gift for the dog lover or just for decoration around the home or office. See Our Adorable Cat Stickers Here

MaterialArticle.Title: Baby Backpack (BROWN):Default Title
Baby Bib:White / One Size
MaterialArticle.Description:
It means so much more with your own pet! Due to popular demand, we can now design YOUR cat, dog or any other pet for special use on our items. You'll love sipping your morning brew from this baby bib featuring your very own fur baby. Or what an amazing gift to give to a loved one! How Does It Work?
Upload a high quality photo of your pet. Remember, we recommend a close and clear photo. Add to Cart and check out. Our expert designers will create a special design using the photo, just like the real life examples here. We'll create and ship your order to you.
Designed, printed and shipped from here in the USA!
This is an AMAZING DEAL and it’s so easy to add your own pet or whatever you like - cats, dogs, horses, birds... even people!
HOW DOES IT WORK?Step 1Simply upload a HIGH QUALITY image of your pet. Make sure it's a clear image and it's been taken on the highest quality setting of your camera. Your pets face MUST be clearly visible and it helps to have its legs or paws out. It's also helpful if they're looking at the camera. We are unable to accept poor quality images as we won't be able to print and give you an excellent end result.You can also leave any instructions for our designer, such as "only use the dog on the right" or "keep paws out". This is optional and we will do our best - however the way these are designed doesn't always allow us to accommodate all requests. Click "Add To Cart" and complete the purchase process. Step 2Our expert designer will work to get your pet inside our special designs. Our designer does each design individually to get you the best results! Step 3Your design goes to our special printing process. Step 4We package and deliver to you as quickly as possible. CAN I ORDER MORE THAN 1 AT A TIME?Yes, it's very easy. Once you've added your first design to the Shopping Cart, simply click back to the product page and repeat the process. CAN I HAVE MORE THAN ONE PET IN THE SAME DESIGN?Yes, we can do our best but remember the size of each pet will not be the same as if you had just one in the design. We still recommend 1 pet per design.
Made from soft polyester fleece; 8.1 oz Fits most newborn to 36 months Machine washable on gentle cycle Dryer safe; low heat tumble dry recommended Ironing not recommended
